caption.title: Rollouts in which the number of people being treated increases linearly until everyone has been treated following untargeted (black and blue lines) and “under age 30” (red and green lines) strategies.
caption.p: The left hand, center, and right-hand column gives outcomes following slow, moderate, and fast increases in the number of people being treated over time. The x-and y-axes are same as in Fig 2 in the main text.
